data.description: Unbelievably gorgeous dream home on 5 acres!!! Extra 3 BR perk site rear of property, 12 ft ceilings, 8 ft doors, stunning kitchen open to LR, private office, utility with doggy shower, double sided fireplace LR/DR, huge covered back porch/patio w/wood burning fireplace, all appliances & storage building stay, basketball court, plenty of deer and wildlife, amazing walk through shower in primary bath with free standing soaker tub, tankless hot water heater.  Showings start Sunday March 13 at 2 PM.
